title: ikanainana
sahitya:
ikanainanA moravina rAdA inakula candrA idi samayamurA

(ikanainanA)



anupallavi



akaLanka nIvE AdhAruDani Ashrayincu nannAdarinca rAdA

(ikanainanA)



caraNam



parama dayA garuDA ninnu prahlAdAdulu vEDaga

karuNinci nIvu kApATa lEdA tirupatipura varada venkatEsha

(ikanainanA)
